            <div>
                <head>Translated parts</head>
                <p xml:id="KR1h0001-start">
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_011-6a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-17T00:19:41.847+09:00">箇人生就的張覺運動這箇叫本性。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_008-31a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-22T17:24:32.159+09:00">孟子說：</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_008-31a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-22T18:48:31.536+09:00"/>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_008-31a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-22T17:27:40.503+09:00"/>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_008-31a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-22T18:48:47.846+09:00"/>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_008-31a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-22T18:49:00.022+09:00"/>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_008-31a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-22T18:49:10.025+09:00"/>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_008-31a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-22T18:49:20.136+09:00"/>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_008-31a.10" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-22T18:49:29.334+09:00"/>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_008-31a.11" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-22T18:49:40.121+09:00"/>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_008-31a.12" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-22T18:49:50.407+09:00"/>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_008-31a.13" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-22T18:50:00.873+09:00"/>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_008-31a.14" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-22T17:30:34.259+09:00"/>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_008-31a.15" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-22T18:50:31.97+09:00"/>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_008-31a.16" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-22T18:51:01.427+09:00"/>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_008-31a.17" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-22T18:51:10.816+09:00"/>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_008-31a.18" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-22T18:51:20.236+09:00"/>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_008-31a.19" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-22T18:51:30.049+09:00"/>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_008-32a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-22T18:51:42.396+09:00"/>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_013-19a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-28T07:00:41.063+09:00">孟子說：</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_013-19a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-28T07:02:04.527+09:00">不可做那心裡所不肯做的不義之事，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_013-19a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-28T07:03:16.325+09:00">不可要那心裡所不要的不義之財，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_013-20a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-28T07:04:06.19+09:00">一個人能夠像這樣就是了。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_003-14a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-03-15T22:22:00.836+09:00">．，『告子曾說過：</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_003-14a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-03-15T22:22:44.147+09:00">「所言於理有未通旳地方，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_003-14a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-03-15T22:22:53.333+09:00">不要再用心去思想．＇</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_003-14a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-03-15T22:23:10.161+09:00">所行於心有未安的地方，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_003-14a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-03-15T22:23:23.845+09:00">不要再求氣來幫助。」</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_003-14a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-03-15T22:23:47.946+09:00">所行於心有未安的地方，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_003-14a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-03-15T22:23:53.957+09:00">不再求氣來幫助，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_003-14a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-03-15T22:24:04.271+09:00">這還可以．</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_003-14a.10" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-03-15T22:24:16.023+09:00">＇所言於理有未通的地方，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_003-14a.11" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-03-15T22:24:28.701+09:00">不再用心去思索，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_003-14a.12" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-03-15T22:24:38.565+09:00">這足不可以。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_003-14a.13" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-03-15T22:25:02.692+09:00">因爲心的趨向就是志，志、是氣的統帥；</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_003-14a.14" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-03-15T22:26:15.2+09:00">氣是志的卒徒，並且充満在人的體內。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_003-14a.15" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-03-15T22:26:53.98+09:00">這志輈向那裹，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_003-14a.16" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-03-15T22:27:00.655+09:00">氣就跟隨到那裏，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_003-14a.17" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-03-15T22:27:10.617+09:00">所以說</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_003-14a.18" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-03-15T22:27:33.636+09:00">「要把握志，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_003-15a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-03-15T22:27:39.901+09:00">同時不擾亂了氣。」』</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_003-15a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-03-15T22:28:05.53+09:00">公孫丑說：『既然說「志就向那裏，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_003-15a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-03-15T22:28:12.709+09:00">氣就跟隨到那裏。」</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_003-15a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-03-15T22:28:23.639+09:00">何必又說</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_003-15a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-03-15T22:28:30.237+09:00">「要把握志，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_003-15a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-03-15T22:28:42.862+09:00">同時不要擾亂了氣」呢！』</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_003-16a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-03-15T22:28:54.232+09:00">孟子說：</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_003-16a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-03-15T22:29:03.361+09:00">『因爲志專一時，氣必隨它走動；</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_003-16a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-03-15T22:29:21.388+09:00">但在氣專一時，也會影響到志。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_003-16a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-03-15T22:29:38.254+09:00">如同一個人，或是跌倒的，或是跑快的，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_003-16a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-03-15T22:29:56.477+09:00">都是氣的作用；</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_003-17a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-03-15T22:30:07.742+09:00">但是反而震盪了他的心志。』</seg>
                </p>
            </div>
